of life-- his and everyone

00:46:44.301 --> 00:46:45.603 align:middle line:85% position:50% size:31%
else's here.

00:46:45.603 --> 00:46:47.338 align:middle line:79% position:48% size:48%
And so with that
in mind, we figured

00:46:47.338 --> 00:46:48.939 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:56%
